{"arkId":"cl010100722","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010100722","modified ":"2025-12-12","title":"Croix \u00e0 double face","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Croix \u00e0 double face"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : gothique (Occident-\u003Emoyen \u00e2ge)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1200 - 1300","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 502 - Suger, Vitrine 28 - Ch\u00e2sses vermicul\u00e9es","room":"Salle 502, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1200,"endYear":1300,"imprecision":"","text":"XIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10013","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; croix d\u0027autel","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Croix l\u00e9g\u00e8rement aur\u00e9ol\u00e9e, potenc\u00e9e, \u00e0, partie inf\u00e9rieure termin\u00e9e en pointe, en cuivre champlev\u00e9, \u00e9maill\u00e9 et dor\u00e9. \r\nLe Christ est rapport\u00e9 en relief cisel\u00e9 et dor\u00e9, tandis que les personnages \u00e0 mi-corps ornant les m\u00e9daillons des potences, ont leurs t\u00eates seules en relief (la Vierge \u00e0 gauche, saint Jean \u00e0 droite, deux anges en bas et en haut). Fond g\u00e9n\u00e9ral \u00e9maill\u00e9 de bleu lapis sem\u00e9 de rinceaux r\u00e9serv\u00e9s et dor\u00e9s, aux extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s fleuronn\u00e9es et parfois \u00e9maill\u00e9es. Titulus r\u00e9serv\u00e9 sur fond turquoise, avec deux lignes superpos\u00e9es. Suppedaneum \u00e9maill\u00e9 bleu lapis, accost\u00e9 de filets blancs. \r\nRevers grav\u00e9 et dor\u00e9, avec rinceaux fleuronn\u00e9s ; sur les potences, les symboles des \u00e9vang\u00e9listes ; au centre, l\u0027Agneau portant la croix, \u00e0 nimbe crucif\u00e8re, entre l\u0027alpha et l\u0027om\u00e9ga.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"23,3","displayDimension":"23,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"12,9","displayDimension":"12,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,7","displayDimension":"0,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : cuivre\r\nTechnique : dor\u00e9 = dorure (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9mail champlev\u00e9 (techniques m\u00e9tal-\u003E\u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux)","placeOfCreation":"Limoges (Limousin-\u003EHaute-Vienne = Haute Vienne)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Claudius C\u00f4te, Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"02\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"16\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"09\/07\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9p